					<head>Halakhah</head>
					<msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85071588" rend="visible">
						<summary>A large fragment of Karaite Sefer ha-mitsṿot.</summary>
						<textLang mainLang="ara" otherLangs="he">Arabic</textLang>
						<msItem rend="visible" class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85071588">
							<locus from="1r" to="102v"/>
							<title xml:lang="ara-Latn-x-lc">Maḳalah 5</title>
							<note>
								<p>Contains parts of Maḳalah 5, treating on forbidden degrees in marriage. Hebrew quotations are also in Arabic characters.</p>
							</note>
						</msItem>
						<msItem rend="">
							<locus from="103r" to="159v"/>
							<title xml:lang="ara-Latn-x-lc">Maḳalah 6</title>
							<note>
								<p>Contains parts of Maḳalah 6 on the laws of inheritance. Hebrew quotations are also in Arabic characters.</p>
							</note>
						</msItem>
						<msItem rend="">
							<locus from="160r" to="167v"/>
							<title xml:lang="ara-Latn-x-lc">Maḳalah </title>
							<note>
								<p>A small fragment of another Maḳalah on unleavened bread on Passover. Hebrew quotations are also in Arabic characters.</p>
							</note>
						</msItem>
					</msContents>
					<physDesc rend="visible">
						<p>Paper codex of the 11th century.</p>
						<objectDesc form="codex">
							<supportDesc material="chart">
								<support>Paper.</support>
								<extent>167 folios <dimensions unit="mm" type="leaf">
										<height>170</height>
										<width>100</width>
									</dimensions>
									<dimensions type="written" unit="mm">
										<height>140</height>
										<width>75</width>
									</dimensions>
								</extent>
								<foliation>
									<p>167 folios (+ 3 unfoliated paper flyleaves at the beginning and 2 at the end). </p>
								</foliation>
								<collation>
									<p>Quires of originally 10 leaves each. The enumeration in Arabic numerals is for the most part preserved.</p>
								</collation>
								<condition>
									<p>Much damaged. Worm-eaten.</p>
									<p>Incomplete. Leaves missing after folio 102, 106, 159.</p>
								</condition>
							</supportDesc>
							<layoutDesc>
